# Agentic Layer Framework

A production-ready Python framework for building **agentic layers** around your codebase using the Google GenAI SDK.

Based on the "Year of Trust" and "Agentic Layer" engineering frameworks, this library provides:

- üéØ **Class/Grade progression system** for measuring agentic capability
- ü§ñ **Multi-agent orchestration** with specialized agents
- üîÑ **Closed-loop self-correcting execution** (Request ‚Üí Validate ‚Üí Resolve)
- üìä **Trust measurement** through tool calling metrics
- üöÄ **AI Developer Workflows (ADWs)** for common patterns

## The Agentic Layer Concept

The **agentic layer** is the new ring around your codebase where you teach your agents to operate your application on your behalf‚Äîas well or better than you ever could.

```
‚îå‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îê
‚îÇ         AGENTIC LAYER               ‚îÇ
‚îÇ  ‚îå‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îê    ‚îÇ
‚îÇ  ‚îÇ    APPLICATION LAYER        ‚îÇ    ‚îÇ
